data.meta_description:
53 likes, 1 comments - oceanarucci on December 9, 2023: "My heartfelt thanks to everyone who took part in our third annual @prestigehk Women of Power celebration on Dec 5. Special thanks to our wonderful speakers: Christina Gae @christinagaw7759, Claudia Shaw @shawclaudia and Camille Cheng @camillelcheng. And congratulations to all 38 new honourees who joined the community this year. ❤️

Video: @samsonjrcdg and @ryanputrant0
